meta-klipper
============

Yocto layer for installing klipper onto the system. 

Dependencies
============

  URI: github.com/Klipper3d/klipper
  branch: master (consider using tag 1.3.0)

  URI: github.com/richardhob/meta-microcontroller
  branch: whinlatter

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-klipper layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-klipper layer to your build
=================================================

1. Add `meta-microcontroller` and its dependencies to your project
2. Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-klipper'

